data.description: Calling 1st time buyers & Investors. Location, location, location! Quaint 3br, 1ba Rambler with great bones situated on a highly desirable private .34 Acres nestled in trees on a dead-end street. 2Br’s on the main, a finished attic space with 3br & an additional finished family/rec area with wood Fireplace in the L. level.  Beautiful hardwood floors complement the living room accented by the wood Fireplace.  Kitchen appliances & new washer/dryer included.  Relax on your deck & watch the wildlife or walk to Parks, Historic downtown Hudson with Restaurants, Boutiques, St. Croix River Park & Marina. The potential is limitless. This home is part of an Estate & Sold AS IS. Professional photos to come.
